{"tid":1838652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：來自獄中的賀年卡：防疫靠自己 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T09:03:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"809e38a3e68ff945501b90734d44effdc16f69f2","tid":1838652,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:02:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200124/BMDLVCDTZZLHOPFHDHCQIZAFMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200124%2FBMDLVCDTZZLHOPFHDHCQIZAFMI%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=b5fd66e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200124%2FBMDLVCDTZZLHOPFHDHCQIZAFMI%2F&h=931f4832\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200124/BMDLVCDTZZLHOPFHDHCQIZAFMI/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：來自獄中的賀年卡：防疫靠自己 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200124/large/1579800524_701b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200124%2Flarge%2F1579800524_701b.gif&h=6084b9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盧建民雖然人在獄中，但仍緊貼時事，繪出多個港人正在面對的情景。<br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n暴動罪被判囚七年嘅盧建民（影攝食）自反送中運動開始，除咗關心抗爭者，仲一直好關心喺前線工作嘅記者。《蘋果》副社長陳沛敏日前就收到影攝食寄自獄中嘅新年賀卡同信件，佢今次主要係祝願我哋記者新年快樂，重叫我哋要出入平安，「不要俾暴警欺負」，睇嚟我哋記者經常畀警察恰嘅形象實在太深入人心啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200124/large/1579801383_319e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200124%2Flarge%2F1579801383_319e.jpg&h=f6ad262b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盧建民<br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n影攝食嘅賀卡剛剛好喺農曆新年前收到，感動嘅不單因為佢關心記者安危，更加喺受牢獄之苦時，仍保持樂觀正面，處處關心香港人同抗爭。佢對香港嘅愛，相信唔比我哋任何一個人少。佢喺信件入面不只載有對記者嘅祝福，亦有好多對香港人嘅提醒同祈望。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200124/large/1579800524_c7ba.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200124%2Flarge%2F1579800524_c7ba.gif&h=8f6f7668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盧建民寄語港人「不遺忘！不善忘！與年青人並肩同行！」<br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n佢寄語港人不要忘記2019年發生嘅事都係源於政府嘅錯，又再提醒我哋「不遺忘！不善忘！」。的確，八方好同意善忘係香港人一直以來嘅特質，希望手足從獄中嘅提醒可以除去大家善忘嘅習慣。信件又畫有三幅插畫，全部都係半年以來抗爭歷歷在目嘅回憶：火海中嘅理大、四點鐘記者會、九億OT錢、和你lunch、太子站、催淚彈等等元素。<br />\n<br />\n除咗香港之外，影攝食亦有關注國際新聞，祈求澳洲山火熄滅，又留意到武漢肺炎來勢洶洶，寄語港人要「靠自己」，小心防疫。話口未完，前日香港就已經出咗兩單確診，中國確診同死亡個案急升，武漢仲封埋城，可見影攝食嘅估計比衞生署更有遠見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n編按：八方會喺農曆年假期收爐，年初五再同讀者見面。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"1af7c36cda14dd1b7357048d759b43fac1dc0098","tid":1838652,"uid":177150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73479496d9b00f32ba1873f0337fded69cd35ed8","tid":1838652,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"畫功唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}